# Class Design

## Movie 
Represents a single movie in the system (title, genre, year, rating).

## UserProfile / User 
Represents a platform user; connects to watch history.

## MovieCatalog 
Manages the full collection of Movie objects and exposes search/filter/recommend by calling our Project 1 functions from `src/movie_lib.py`. Includes validation and max size.

## WatchLog
Records user watch events (start, finish, rate) with timestamps.

## AnalyticsDashboard 
Uses movies + watch events to produce reports (most watched, trending, accuracy).
